1. The xpad module need to be installed via menuconfig
    a. In menu config go to device drivers->inputs->joysticks->microsoft xbox controller support
    b. Enable the driver as a loadable module (M) and save the configuration
    Before loading the module, create the necessary directory structure:

    mkdir -p /lib/modules/$(uname -r)/kernel/drivers/input/joystick

    Then copy the compiled `xpad.ko` module to this directory:

    cp  /lib/modules/$(uname -r)/kernel/drivers/input/joystick/
2. To compile the code:
    a. qmake
    b. make
   
3. In tera term or serial port type in:
    a.insmod /lib/modules/*/kernel/drivers/input/joytick/xpad.ko
    b. chmod +x spaceinvaders
    c. ./spaceinvaders